{"tid":446450,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE仔有野想向各位巴打請教","createTime":"2017-10-24T10:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T17:35:57.000Z","uid":149930,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ade08cfcf69060d3ffc40848888d5dd7faaefd5d","tid":446450,"uid":149930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟IVE岩岩開左兩個月左右 發現自己揀錯科(環球商貿其中一科)<br />\n<br />\n個科基本上用全英文教(讀寫講) 只係極少量用中文補充<br />\n<br />\n發現自己已經脫哂節 所以想話轉科讀<br />\n<br />\n小弟一直都對商科有興趣 市場會計銀行呢啲又唔想讀<br />\n<br />\n唯一一科睇中既係工商管理 但睇好多評論都話係伏科 話唔好讀<br />\n<br />\n但我係商科又搵唔到其他專科自己有興趣(無興趣你根本唔會想讀)<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴打 知唔知IVE有咩科係用中文教學(講解)得note係英文<br />\n<br />\n請各位巴打指點迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b288eeecc4ee50bd41dc2d39ae80dfa5de4f409","tid":446450,"uid":58583,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"ive商科全部都係狗科 出黎搵雞碎 讀邊科都一樣<br />\n<br />\n得9k 至10k 起跳 做幾年先加條毛<br />\n<br />\n你係對商業有興趣做生意既話就quit 再白手打拚啦<br />\n<br />\n除非你真係對D theory 好有興趣<br />\n<br />\n如果你係後者我會覺得好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 sem 3頂唔順quit左"},{"pid":"ec5b029d79c0e66757e7bd30dac527d4aa2559b8","tid":446450,"uid":398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"大部分都英文教咖wo"},{"pid":"706faab617c589857b2e42a8a10c1a9ee7a73be8","tid":446450,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf32f4edee5f682724e42568be5488d5aea3fe6c","tid":446450,"uid":70472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"想用中文讀high dip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係去台灣一係去中國，就算讀中藥1個Sem入面都係得1-2科係用中文教，其他科都係英文"},{"pid":"23bd3f3ecde4c0662378085efc3ef1ac5ed31f8e","tid":446450,"uid":29585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"工程啦"},{"pid":"07c4312dd174b3cade72dee8b09869729a26624a","tid":446450,"uid":70472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"同埋而家先想轉科應該太遲，9月果陣申請仲有機會，一係quit左佢下年再報過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5ab4360bf2b82c2999bc0e5f0d5e0bbd543784","tid":446450,"uid":128525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"我上hrm 個hd，上好多堂都係用中文講多"},{"pid":"1ca61d394cdc9b584a3d07097f0a000168ae8fc1","tid":446450,"uid":82175,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"對咩商業有興趣呀 <br />\n會計咁實際又唔岩<br />\n廢柴畢業請你做管理層呀？<br />\n有料你唔洗IVE 去IVY啦<br />\n 一係咪晒錢 推架木頭車賣牛雜"},{"pid":"8ec88ea679df18aa6ab6fee8317835aa07e01040","tid":446450,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"就算你過到ive 出到黎做野咪又係英文"},{"pid":"072df5ca180c26b2ed5ee081beeb1277c9225109","tid":446450,"uid":188,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"Ive 英文都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗轉咩住<br />\n<br />\n你驗腦先好d"},{"pid":"3a1195d67c5af2ec761926e6bd66c834cab74bf7","tid":446450,"uid":149930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想用中文讀high dip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係去台灣一係去中國，就算讀中藥1個Sem入面都係得1-2科係用中文教，其他科都係英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解網上面啲人又有啲用中文講解 note係英文既 定以前先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14db6125f706e7c954e840c511139a20bc4bfac0","tid":446450,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"ive商科就算鳩數啦 邊科唔係一樣<br />\n三大商科都未必個個搵到工啦"},{"pid":"3e59e1c733ceb9d5952eefaef4af5c547aba17b9","tid":446450,"uid":149930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上hrm 個hd，上好多堂都係用中文講多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慘在唔知ive係咪呢 因為我個科係環球商貿用英文我明<br />\n<br />\n但其他唔會都係全英文掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849eedcad2da694e6e8e5b252d439d4f56171d23","tid":446450,"uid":72622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"讀ba 已經好簡單 轉其他我諗仲跟唔上仲辛苦 <br />\n  坦白講ba出到黎咪又係做文員仔 唔係話睇低人地 係真係冇咩用"},{"pid":"a12c74bb05b6b14a73858c10e10c284844d7ce27","tid":446450,"uid":149930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對咩商業有興趣呀 <br />\n會計咁實際又唔岩<br />\n廢柴畢業請你做管理層呀？<br />\n有料你唔洗IVE 去IVY啦<br />\n 一係咪晒錢 推架木頭車賣牛雜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲野唔係話實際就得 你無心/無興趣去讀<br />\n再實際對你黎講都無用<br />\n好似法律醫療藥劑都好實際架<br />\n但唔代表你一定有興趣讀同讀到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce52798f3246663f66bb90e6d64cd31380586c8","tid":446450,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"英文note 中文講書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72507505f13d998d75498c367b4ecf3c5cbfa8eb","tid":446450,"uid":149930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ive 英文都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗轉咩住<br />\n<br />\n你驗腦先好d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢照住份野讀 讀完當教完<br />\n<br />\n我根本唔知佢教緊啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb66fc63a54ad10199662b4ade628c90cbe6ba6","tid":446450,"uid":140109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"IVE工程科 10成中文教，不過考試英文卷（不過唔會成為障礙）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fe94296c46cd0219792ab10c560a2879b183aa","tid":446450,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Iv